<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Freely</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/app.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/semantic/dist/semantic.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Cutive+Mono" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/semantic/dist/semantic.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="ui basic center aligned inverted segment" id="jumbotron"> <!--Sometimes I question my choice of going with Semantic instead of Bootstrap...-->
        <h1 class="ui header" id="site-title">Freely</h1>
        <h3 class="ui header">Daily freewriting for a better life.</h3>
        <div class="ui hidden divider"></div>
        <a href="/register" class="ui huge primary button">Sign up for free<i class="ui right arrow icon"></i></a><br>
        <% if (!currentUser) { %>
            <a href="/login" class="ui secondary button">Log In</a>
        <% } else { %>
            <a href="/entries/new" class="ui secondary button">Log In</a>
        <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="ui lander-padded container">
        <div class="ui hidden divider"></div>
        <div class="ui center aligned very padded raised segment">
            <h2 class="ui header"><em>Producing writing is not so much like filling a basin or pool once, but rather getting water to keep flowing through till finally it runs clear.</em></h2>
            <p class="ui right floated small header">-Peter Elbow, <i>freewriting pioneer</i></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ui basic segment">
        <div class="ui stackable grid container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="six wide column">
                <div class="ui very padded basic segment">
                    <h2 class="ui header">Freely encourages you to freewrite every day.</h2>
                    <p class="landing-p">Research shows that daily freewriting can help the mind calm down, process emotions and boost creativity. Writer Julia Cameron is known for her advocacy of doing three pages of stream-of-consciousness writing every morning. Freely is the perfect online platform for you to start and maintain a daily writing habit.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ten wide column">
              <!--<img alt="Cool video explaining the product will go here" class="ui large bordered rounded image" style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 15em">-->
              <img src="/images/streak-showcase.png" alt="Streak notification showing the writer they've written for 23 consecutive days" class="ui massive bordered image" id="darkborder">
              <h3 class="ui center aligned header">Write every day to build streaks and keep the momentum going.</h3>
              <div class="ui stackable grid">
                  <div class="eight wide column">
                      <img src="/images/tagshelp1.png" class="ui large bordered image" id="darkborder">
                  </div>
                  <div class="eight wide column">
                      <img src="/images/tagshelp2.png" class="ui large bordered image" id="darkborder">
                  </div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="ui center aligned header">Organize past entries with tags.</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
