        <h4 class="ui horizontal header divider">
            <a href="#">The Evidence</a>
        </h4>
        <div class="ui lander-padded text container">
              <h2 class="ui header">Case study: expressing emotions leads to a calmer mind and healthier emotions</h2>
              <p class="landing-p">A 2007 UCLA study focused on the reaction of the amygdala, the brain’s alarm system, when participants were shown pictures of angry or fearful faces. Participants described each face’s emotion as it appeared, and their brain activity was studied using fMRI. Matthew D. Lieberman, associate professor of psychology at UCLA: “When you attach the word 'angry,' you see a decreased response in the amygdala”.</p>
              <p class="landing-p">Labelling emotions also activated a part of the brain associated with emotion processing and self-inhibition. These results have practical application when it comes to emotional health. Lieberman continues, <strong>"When you put feelings into words, you seem to be hitting the brakes on your emotional responses… Putting our feelings into words helps us heal.”</strong> (UCLA).</p>
        </div>
    
    <!--<div class="ui huge message lander-padded">-->
    <!--    <div class="ui hidden divider"></div>-->
    <!--    <div class="ui center aligned container">-->
    <!--        <p class="">Research shows that freewriting has several benefits:</p>-->
    <!--    </div>-->
    <!--</div>-->
    <div class="ui center aligned inverted stackable middle aligned grid segment" id="ten-padded">
        <div class="ten wide column">
            <h2 class="ui inverted header">Start your freewriting journey now.</h2>
            <p>Signing up while the app is in beta means your account is free, forever. No ads, no restrictions. <br>Thank you for believing in this project.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ui six wide column inverted left aligned segment">
            <div class="ui container">
                <% if (success && success.length > 0) { %>
                <div class="ui positive message thing" style="margin-top: 5em">
                    <i class="close icon"></i>
                    <div class="header">
                        Success
                    </div>
                    <p><%= success %></p>
                </div>
                <% } %>
                <% if (error && error.length > 0) { %>
                <div class="ui negative message thing" style="margin-top: 5em">
                    <i class="close icon"></i>
                    <div class="header">
                        Error
                    </div>
                    <p><%= error %></p>
                </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <form class="ui inverted form" id="main-form" action="/register" method="POST">
                <div class="field">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="username" name="username">
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <input type="password" placeholder="password" name="password">
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <input type="password" placeholder="repeat password" name="password2">
                </div>
                <div class="ui left floated field">
                    <div class="ui checkbox">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="terms">
                        <label>I agree to the <a href="/terms" target="_blank">terms and conditions</a></label>
                    </div>
                    <button class="ui right floated primary button">Sign Up</button>
                </div>
                <div class="ui error message"></div>
                <div class="ui hidden divider"></div>
                <p style="color: red; text-align: center">This site is currently in beta. Please read the terms and conditions carefully before signing up.</p>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

<script>

//If there's a login error message, scroll down to login form

$('.ui.form')
    .form({
        fields: {
            username: {
                identifier: 'username',
                rules: [
                    {
                        type   : 'empty',
                        prompt : 'Please enter a username'
                    }
                ]
            },
            password: {
                identifier: 'password',
                rules: [
                    {
                        type   : 'empty',
                        prompt : 'Please enter a password'
                    },
                    {
                        type: 'match[password2]',
                        prompt: "Passwords must match"
                    }
                ]
            },
            terms: {
                identifier: 'terms',
                rules: [
                {
                        type   : 'checked',
                        prompt : 'You must agree to the terms and conditions'
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
    })
;
        
$('.message .close')
  .on('click', function() {
    $(this)
      .closest('.message')
      .transition('fade')
    ;
  })
;

var elmnt = document.querySelector(".thing");
elmnt.scrollIntoView();
</script>
